graph LR
    subgraph Primary Site [Active DC - Primary Site]
        subgraph Primary HA Cluster
            P_ANN[Active NameNode] <--> P_SNN[Standby NameNode]
            P_ANN --> P_DN[DataNodes]
        end
    end

    subgraph DR Site [Recovery DC - Standby Site]
        subgraph DR HA Cluster
            DR_ANN[Active NameNode] <--> DR_SNN[Standby NameNode]
            DR_ANN --> DR_DN[DataNodes]
        end
    end

    %% DistCp replication
    P_DN -->|Asynchronous Replication via DistCp / MapReduce Job| DR_DN
    P_ANN -.->|Metadata Backup Snapshots via DistCp| DR_ANN

    Note over P_DN, DR_DN: Periodic incremental delta runs sync HDFS blocks.<br/>Hadoop DistCp runs as MapReduce job to stream files.
    Note over DR_ANN: DR NameNode is in ACTIVE state locally,<br/>but data volumes are read-only<br/>until failover is activated.
